  <brief_title>Cerebral Tissue Oxygenation in Very Low Birthweight Infants in the First 3 Days of Life</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cerebral Tissue Oxygen Saturation in Preterm Neonates Below 1500g Birth Weight During the First 72 Hours</official_title>
  <sponsors>
